{
  "stem": "12003.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She had classes in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A Jewish woman.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She certainly did not look Jewish, and she-- she was a young person at that time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She must have been in her very early 20s.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In ghetto, in-- you know, it-- it was-- there was a public place where you could sort of perform and gather a lot of people, and she took part of it.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we used to have certain time of the day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She used to give us lessons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wasn't the only one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were a few of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She had, like, a little Victrola with a record.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it felt good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It felt that pretty soon I'd be able to perform in the-- in the free world.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was learning.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was looking toward future.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was-- for some reason, I always knew deep in my heart that I will live, that I will come through.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was hard to when I was separated from the family, from my parents and my sisters and my brother.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I was always shelter, whatever camp I was, by the adults around me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they even try to give me their extra ration so I would be better nourished, because, you know, our rations were very meager.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, they weren't even fit for-- we don't treat like-- animals like this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, there-- there were songs that were composed in the ghettos.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember them now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] No, I don't remember them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had, like, a little group.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were Polish songs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly what songs they were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I know toward the end, we always sang [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we knew the words to it in Polish, and my sisters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
